content: Hi 🥱...3..2..1..here you go,
HAPPPPYYYYYYYYYYYY BIIRRRTHHHHDAAAAAYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYYY!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! VERY VERRYY HAPPPIEST BIRTHDAAAAYYYYY TO YOUUUUU 🥳🎉🤪

🤔 kaaffii halka lg raha hy, wait... meri taraf sy ek chhoti si cute aur sweet wish 😊..May your day be filled with laughter, endless joy, and surprises as amazing as you are. You deserve nothing but the best always.

btw 😁 mai apni aadat sy kaisy baaz aa skti hon? Tu jaanta hai na mujhe, ek chhoti wish kafi nahi hoti. So here comes my typical long lecture style wish 🙃... Happy Birthday once again! Tujhe meri taraf se bohot saari duaen aur best wishes. May this year bring you peace, success, and happiness jo tu deserve karta hai. Har nayi subah tere liye ek nayi hope aur ek naya reason laye smile karne ka. Stay blessed, stay happy, and hamesha isi tarah mast aur special rehna.

On your special day, I just want to remind you how much you mean. Zindagi mein kai log milte hain but very few feel as rare as you. May this birthday be the start of something beautiful for you. Jo bhi plans, dreams aur wishes tere hain, un sab ka door nahi bas pass hone ka waqt shuru ho jaye. Aur yaad rakh, I’ll always cheer for you.
Happy Birthday once again, bestie! 🎂🎉 May your day be full of good vibes, laughter, and lots of cake (aur thodi si meri yaad bhi 😏).
Har birthday ek reminder hai ke tu aur zyada annoying hone wala hai 🤪 Happy Birthday!

Kabhi realize kiya hai tu mere liye kitna special hai? Tu bas ek naam ya ek dost nahi… tu meri zindagi ka woh hissa hai jo mujhe lagta hai Allah ne specially mere liye banaya. Har message, har baat, har choti si cheez mujhe remind karti hai ki main lucky hoon tujhe paake. Aur agar kabhi future mein hum door bhi ho gaye na (jo main chahti nahi 😔), toh bhi yaad rakhna — tu meri zindagi ka woh chapter hoga jisko main kabhi band nahi kar paungi.

“Your birthday isn’t only about candles and cake. It’s a psychological anchor, proof of survival, growth, memories, and everything that shaped you. I’m just lucky I get to witness this checkpoint in your journey. Happy Birthday 🌟”
Teri birthday pe tujh se ek promise le leti hoon: hamesha mast rehna aur kabhi dull mat hona 🙃

Main kabhi kabhi sochti hoon… kitna ajeeb hota agar hum kabhi milte hi nahi? Mujhe lagta hai zindagi kaafi adhuri hoti, jaise ek important rang missing ho. Tu ne meri duniya ko aisi jagmagahat di hai jahan main khud ko zyada achi samajhne lagi hoon, zyada strong feel karti hoon. Jo cheez mujhe khud mein pasand nahi thi, tu ne unhe bhi accept karne ka jazba diya. Tu bas ek dost nahi...tu meri strength, meri smile aur meri best memory hai.

Imagine me standing outside your window with a megaphone 📢 at 3 AM, screaming: “WAKE UPPPPPP! IT’S YOUR BIRTHDAAAAAYYYYYYYY” 🤯🎂🎉. Neighbors hate me 🏠😤, dogs are barking 🐶🐾, and I don’t even care 🤪—because that’s how important today is. HAPPY BIRTHDAYYYYY, YOU LEGEND 🏆✨!
Happy Birthday! Aur yaad rakh, abhi 250 aur messages baaki hain, patience level test hoga aaj tera 😌

I don’t say this often, but you really do make everything better. Even when you annoy me, somehow I’m still grateful for you....you’re proof that not all chaos is bad. Sometimes I wish I could record our conversations; they’re priceless. Imagine rewatching them years later—I’d laugh just as hard again. Honestly, I wouldn’t trade this bond for anything. You might think I exaggerate, but I mean every single word. If time froze right now, I’d still be happy, just because I’d be here—annoying you. You’re stuck with me, and honestly… I’m glad you are. Out of millions of people, I somehow ended up with you, and that’s special. Don’t forget: you’re not just my favorite person—you’re my favorite story. If birthdays were galaxies, I’d fill them all just to celebrate you. And even after 300 messages, I still have more to say, because you’re worth every single one. You’re not just part of my story—you ARE the story. No matter what, I’m glad this story has you in it. So yeah… Happy Birthday, you chaotic masterpiece. Thank you—for existing, for being you, for staying. And P.S.? Don’t think this ends here… I’ll keep spamming you, because 300 messages will never be enough to show how much you mean. So buckle up—you’re not escaping me anytime soon. Here’s to another year of chaos, laughter, and endless spam. Happy Birthday again, my one and only favorite headache 🎉💖
Out of all the days, today just feels warm and perfect because it’s YOUR day 🌸. I hope every moment makes you smile, because you really deserve nothing but joy.
Dekho... aaj tu officially ek saal aur purana ho gaya... matlab budhaa pan officially shuru 😂

Happy Birthday! Ekdum honestly bolun toh, tu kabhi kabhi mujhe itna annoy karta hai ki mai sochti hoon tujhe ek thappad maar du 😏. Lekin saath hi tu mujhe itna support karta hai ki mujhe realize hota hai – irritating log hi asli mein sabse close hote hain. Tu sirf friend nahi, ek dum family jaisa hai. Aur family ko wish karne ka style bhi alag hota hai, heartfelt and full of love.

text: Roses are red, gifts are cool… but none of them can beat my birthday spam duel

content: Sometimes I feel tu jaan bujh ke mujhe overthink karata hai, just to see my reaction 🤔… but aaj ke din mai bas simple kehna chahti hoon: Happy Birthday, troublemaker! 🎉
Aj na tere naam ka ek naya constellation ban gaya hai… star-boy 🌌😂

Aik chhoti si kahani: ek din ek insaan meri life mein aaya. Pehle mujhe laga normal banda hai, but dheere dheere pata chala ki ye banda thoda alag hai (shaed pora pagal hai 🤣) irritating bhi, funny bhi, caring bhi. Aur dheere dheere wo banda ekdum best friend ban gaya. Guess what? Wo banda tu hai. Aur aaj uska birthday hai. So Happy Birthday, dost! Tu meri kahani ka best chapter hai.
Har saal ek reminder hota hai ke tu grow kar raha hai. Aur mai bas ye wish karti hoon ki tu grow kare sirf age mein nahi, par happiness, wisdom, aur success mein bhi. Happy Birthday, best friend!
“AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA—sorry, just had to scream your birthday energy out loud 🤪🎊 HAPPY BIRTHDAYYYYYYY!!”

text: My actual face right now wishing you… PURE MADNESS LEVEL BIRTHDAY!!!

content: Okay, listen...if happiness had a face, it would literally be you right now because of how much joy you’ve brought into my life. 🥹 You don’t even realize it, but your existence is the kind of blessing people write stories about. Happy birthday, my precious headache, my walking chaos, and my favorite reason to smile.
Har birthday tere liye ek nayi chapter shuru karta hai. Bas dua hai ke ye chapter best ho – full of success, full of peace, aur full of laughs. Aur haan, meri bakbak bhi zaroor shamil ho 😁
Happy Birthday to the only person jo ‘typing…’ pe 10 minute waste karta hai.

Kabhi realize karta hai ke tu kitna irritating hai? Aur phir bhi main tere saath kyu hoon? 😂 Kyunki irritate karne ke saath tu meri life ka sabse precious banda bhi hai. On your birthday, I just want to say tu perfect nahi hai, but tu apne tareeke se ekdum special hai. Aur mere liye bas wahi matter karta hai. Happy Birthday 🎉🤗
Plot twist: Every candle you blow today 🎂🕯️ isn’t just a wish—it’s a signal flare telling the universe to send you EXTRA happiness ✨💫😂. HAPPY BIRTHDAYYYYYYYYY 🎉🎉🎉.
Promise note: next birthday, I’m breaking this record. Zyada wishes, zyada surprises—prepare your cheeks for extra smiling 😏.

If happiness was confetti 🎊, I just threw a truckload of it on you 🚛💥🤣. If love was cake 🍰, I just delivered 100 layers. If friendship was a balloon 🎈, your sky would be FULL by now 🌌✨. HAPPY BIRTHDAAAYYYYYYYYYYYY , you chaos magnet 🤪🎉.

Happy Birthday! Tu ekdum special hai mere liye. Tere bina meri chats, meri bakbak, aur meri daily life ekdum adhoori hai. May this year bring you all the peace aur happiness jo tu deserve karta hai.
